ParallelChunk.en:
It is obvious that health services form an integral part of European social infrastructure; 
          if
         anything specifically typifies Europe and sets it apart out from elsewhere, it is the way in which we make a high level of health care available to all citizens, irrespective of their personal backgrounds.

ParallelChunk.fr:
